summary: This document is a bank statement from Fifth Third Bank for the account of Disco Scientia Corporation for the period of July 1, 2017, to July 31, 2017. It details the account's beginning and ending balances, service charges, and criteria for waiving those charges.
keyFacts: The beginning balance for the account was $231.26.
A standard monthly service charge of $11.00 was withdrawn on 07/13/17.
The account did not meet the criteria for waiving the service charge based on average balance or credit card spending.
The document includes an introductory offer for business checks from Harland Clarke.
